{"tid":2027651,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩幫我推..","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T18:11:07.000Z","uid":317835,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e34835a16c78a2bcbf45bf013a3b55146afc7b49","tid":2027651,"uid":317835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"係2019年10月4日 蒙面惡法立法之日 我等香港獨立自主人士經已為對抗中共政櫂 宣讀香港臨時政府宣言 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AQP2EaEsSJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAQP2EaEsSJk&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3b30ca69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AQP2EaEsSJk</a><br />\n時至今日 我等仍然為此共同目標而奮鬥及努力 <br />\n<br />\n你地呢班係10月4號我地讀出黎仲屌緊我地既人  而家你地有冇一絲絲既後悔 <br />\n香港獨立.唯一出路.<br />\n我請求所有身處係外國既手足 <br />\n立即連繫唔同國家.唔同州份既手足<br />\n成立公司 有系統 公開及透明<br />\n打住正統既旗幟 組裝軍隊  反攻中國共產黨<br />\n要靠.始終要靠我地自己<br />\n我相信 黎得外國既手足 每個都起碼揹住幾條罪<br />\n我曾經都有諗過.黎到外國 就放低所有香港既事 <br />\n事實證明. 我依然會為香港發生既所有事而牽腸掛肚 <br />\n我相信...你地都會   <br />\n不日..我將會在海外公開地成立反共組織 到時請他國手足互相聯絡 商討下一步 <br />\n<br />\n身處香港既手足....請平安 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLhW976.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLhW976.jpg&h=30912396&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f934da76e473a3410b1e0858f7f99c29964fc25d","tid":2027651,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"Posh"},{"pid":"29145fe8f98d317cdc005477544850ee8c501554","tid":2027651,"uid":317835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f934da76e473a3410b1e0858f7f99c29964fc25d","tid":2027651,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"Posh"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"多謝手足幫我推"},{"pid":"d7c9cfa980c876b29dc8d12e7855e75a3dfcef66","tid":2027651,"uid":140345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03028